<item>
            <title>[LU-4769] Test failure conf-sanity test_38: umount of MDS on ZFS failed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4769</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Nathaniel Clark &amp;lt;nathaniel.l.clark@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/19440768-a91d-11e3-96a3-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/19440768-a91d-11e3-96a3-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/1ab639ac-ab31-11e3-8617-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/1ab639ac-ab31-11e3-8617-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/f45565c0-ab04-11e3-a41c-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/f45565c0-ab04-11e3-a41c-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_38 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;mount -t zfs lustre-mdt1/mdt1 /tmp/mds1 failed (1)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: conf-sanity 38&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is a regression introduced by 162b62cdb04fcf14df75c5b3b8d30616f4104220&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/9184&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/9184&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
